Add public key on the server
Copy private key file at ~/.ssh/xxxx.pem
edit ~/.ssh/config file:
  Host xx.xx.xx.xx
   HostName xx.xx.xx.xx
   IdentityFile ~/.ssh/xxxx.pem
   User xxx
   
   
 ssh-add -l // to check added ssh key
 ssh-add // will add all private keys under HOME/.ssh/, make chmod 400 for private key files
